import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

img_array = np.load('/content/drive/MyDrive/Colab/Detecting_and_Classifying_Car_Damage/results/dent/numpy/image_0106.npy')
mask_array = np.load('/content/drive/MyDrive/Colab/Detecting_and_Classifying_Car_Damage/results/dent/numpy/label_0106.npy')

plt.subplot(131)
plt.imshow(img_array, cmap='gray')
plt.title('image')

plt.imshow(mask_array, cmap='gray')
plt.title('mask')

plt.subplot(133)
plt.imshow(output_array, cmap='gray')
plt.title('output')

plt.show()
